name: Got Health?
body:
### Welcome to Got Health?

Got Health? makes it easy to view the fitness data stored in Apple Health, written by any other fitness app, the Apple Watch, or the Apple Pedometer app.

privacy policy: This app allows you to read information from the Apple Health App. It also allows you to send your Apple Health App information to anyone you choose via email. The app neither saves nor transmits you information to anyone, other than the previously mentioned email that can only be sent to an email address you select.



for support contact dev dot flacco at gmail dot com
